Add foundational UI components and structure for the creative studio application

This commit introduces a comprehensive set of UI components, including buttons, modals, navigation elements, and form controls, along with the initial HTML structure and a service worker for the PWA. It also configures the application's manifest file and sets up routing within `App.tsx`.

